# Satellite working tree for shop-demodata-ce. Cloned at top level (not in
# vendor/) so PhpStorm's Composer integration doesn't auto-exclude it; the
# entrypoint then symlinks vendor/o3-shop/shop-demodata-ce -> here so
# composer/code paths keep working unchanged.
